 patents a difficult task.
 This specificity of patents content led us to explore a method of term
 diversification selection for query expansion (the diversification here
 arise to select terms not only similar to the query to avoid the effect
 of its ambiguity).
 More specifically, we propose a new algorithm for query expansion based
 on the Maximal Marginal Relevance (MMR) 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
